content: Climbing has become my favourite thing. I'm thinking about it all day, watching videos, practicing hanging on whatever. Going late on Wednesdays to the gym in Westgate for the last 2 hours before it closes. This week I even went on Friday and spent my rest time coding. I've been a total of 6 times now and managed to send a v3. Woop Woop. Getting some shoes as soon as they go on sale
